                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I had seen it about three minutes before—she had to go through the shop to go up stairs—there was no carpet—I had told her she was not likely to suit me—she was only one week with me—I wanted her to go at a fortnight's warning, but she would not.</p>
